39:54.158 --> 39:56.460 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
SERGIO AVILA-VILLEGAS,
Arizona-Sonora Desert
Museum: Nature has no borders.

39:56.494 --> 39:58.262 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Nature knows no political
boundaries.

39:58.295 --> 40:00.664 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
WILLIAM BRANGHAM: Sergio
Avila-Villegas is
